This paper is about using transfer learning and multi-domain ensembles to improve biomedical translation. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and computer vision (cs.CV).
